item.title: CVE-2021-20654|2024-08-03T17:45:45.121Z -- wekan%20team -- wekan
item.description: Wekan, open source kanban board system, between version 3.12 and 4.11, is vulnerable to multiple stored cross-site scripting. This is named 'Fieldbleed' in the vendor's site.
